SRC: What are friends? We often talk about the topic with others. I think friends are those people who can help you when you are in trouble. Don’t forget the saying, “A friend in need is a friend indeed.” Friends can tell you your mistakes, though what they say is hard for you to listen to. You can share
TGT: 朋友是什么？我们经常和别人谈论这个话题。我认为朋友就是在你遇到困难时能够帮助你的人。不要忘记那句谚语：“患难见真情。”朋友会指出你的错误，尽管他们说的话可能让你难以接受。你可以和朋友分享你的快乐、烦恼和忧虑。还有人说：“没有朋友，寸步难行。”所以我朋友对我们来说非常重要。我希望能交到尽可能多的朋友。

[Text]
What are friends? We often talk about the topic with others. I think friends are those people who can help you when you are in trouble. Don’t forget the saying, “A friend in need is a friend indeed.” Friends can tell you your mistakes, though what they say is hard for you to listen to. You can share your happiness, trouble, and worry with friends. Someone also says, “You can’t walk any step without a friend.” So I think friends are very important to us. I would like to make as many friends as possible.}], model=qwen3-max}
